snippet.textDisplay:
I am a warriors fan, and I feel so sad watching them loosing many games, but still I am faithful they can redeem next season
But hearing the news of Kobe Bryant's suddenly death, I can't even imagine how it just happened quickly. I felt like I've been hit by something hard faster than the lightning. Now I'm in tears and thinking how am I supposed to sleep knowing that the Black Mamba is already gone. And the worst part is he died with 7 or 8 people including his daughter Gigi. I am still crying, remembering the highlights, greetings, and even the trash talk. I wonder how he comfort his daughter before their last glance to this world. I will forever miss you Kobe. I will pray for the peace of your soul and your family.
Mamba will live forever.😢😿😥😭
